Package compiler

Interface Summary
Statement A STATEMENT is an object that is nested inside of Blocks.
 

Class Summary
Block A block consisting of zero or more statements.
Expression An expression consisting of a single Term, followed by zero or more ADDOP TERM pairs.
Factor A factor consisting of a single expression object encapsulated in parentheses OR a DIGITS as defined by Token OR an IDENTIFIER as defined by Token
GameCommand GameCommand is a class that holds the Game Command itself, as defined by Token and the parameters to that game command call.
GameFunction GameCommand is a class that holds the Game Function itself, as defined by Token and the parameters to that game function call.
IfElse An IFELSE consisting of an Expression CONDITION Expression triplet where CONDITION is defined in Token Also contains the if Block and else Block of code.
IfOnly An IF statement consisting of an Expression CONDITION Expression triplet where CONDITION is defined in Token Also contains the if Block of code.
MainProgram A block of MAIN{} code with any number of statements between the opening and closing braces
Parameters An ordered list of parameters.
ReturnStatement A RETURN statement consisting of the variable that is to be used as the return value.
Routine A Routine is an entire Robot Wars program represented by a list of Subroutines and a singleton MainProgram
Start  
Subroutine A SUBROUTINE consisting of the subroutine's IDENTIFIER as defined by Token and it's parameter list Also contains the subroutine's Block of code.
Term A term consisting of a single Factor, followed by zero or more MULTOP FACTOR pairs.
TextFile Wrapper class that is used to pull a text file from hard disk into memory.
Token Tokens are built from terminal symbols in the Robot Wars language.
VariableAssignment An variable assignment consisting of the variable a given value is to be saved to.
While A WHILE statement consisting of an Expression CONDITION Expression triplet where CONDITION is defined in Token Also contains the while Block of code.
 

Enum Summary
Token.TokenType Collection of token types.
